# Scroll back : Shift+{PageUp,PageDown}
wget https://st.suckless.org/patches/scrollback/st-scrollback-20201205-4ef0cbd.diff
patch < ./patches/scrollback/st-scrollback-20201205-4ef0cbd.diff 
cp config.def.h config.h
make clean install

